&lt;p&gt;FanDuel is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Campaign Strategy Director&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Sportsbook Campaign Strategy team. In this role, you will develop and execute marketing campaign strategies that drive business growth across FanDuel’s key verticals, working closely with cross-functional partners including product, creative, commercial, and analytics teams.&amp;nbsp; You’ll be responsible for translating insights and commercial objectives into compelling campaign strategies and creative briefs, ensuring alignment with our brand identity and business goals. This is a strategic leadership position where you will drive campaign effectiveness, own measurement strategies, and lead continuous improvement in how we plan, execute, and learn from our marketing initiatives. You will serve as a key thought partner in shaping the role of sports marketing as a business enabler, identifying opportunities for innovation and partner activation, and fostering strong relationships with both internal teams and external agency partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition to the specific responsibilities outlined above, employees may be required to perform other such duties as assigned by the Company. This ensures operational flexibility and allows the Company to meet evolving business needs.&lt;/p&gt;
