&lt;li&gt;Coordinate key deliverables across teams to ensure alignment on strategy, timelines, output expectations, operating from a single shared playbook&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver post campaign analysis and data-driven learnings, translating insights into actionable recommendations that optimize future campaigns and drive continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
